replies.body:
I really like what you've done with this alpha. It may not be the same later, but it is really REALLY smooth, the animations are great and overall it looks fantastic. The one thing I noticed was the League of Legend icon leading to the menu that disappeared, how do you get back to the menu to see the news or spectate random people? What will be the main menu? What is the first screen when you login? I also find the menu to access a match   kindaconfusing if you're a beginner, but after a few games they'll get used to it.

Other than those questions, it looks amazing, that's what this game deserves. Great job!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
